        <h2 class="mt-6 font-display text-3xl font-extrabold leading-tight text-ink sm:text-4xl">
          I didn’t start in data — I started by running a business <span class="text-gold">on it</span>.
        </h2>
        <img
          src="/brand/avatar-laptop.png"
          alt="Illustration of Matías Rossi working at his laptop"
